      • bestGuessFromString

        public static ClassName bestGuessFromString(String classNameString)
        Returns a new ClassName instance for the given fully-qualified class name string. This method assumes that the input is ASCII and follows typical Java style (lower-case package names, upper-camel-case class names) and may produce incorrect results or throw IllegalArgumentException otherwise. For that reason, fromClass(Class) and fromClass(Class) should be preferred as they can correctly create ClassName instances without such restrictions.
